name: Developer Workflows and Trends Students can use!
description: In this livestream, with Ruby Sattar being the host, we discussed some developer trends and workflows that would benefit students and juniors. I spoke about some noteworthy trends in web development, namely responsive web design, single page applications and progressive web apps. This was my first time doing a livestream and I really enjoyed the process getting to that point and I'm glad I got most of the things right.
